    <title type="html"><![CDATA[sublime利用snippet生成代码模版]]></title>
    <link href="http://ztblog.github.io/blog/2013/10/23/sublime-snippet/"/>
    <updated>2013-10-23T14:20:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://ztblog.github.io/blog/2013/10/23/sublime-snippet</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><code>tools-&gt;New Snippet</code>新建一个snippet，保存为**.sublime-snippet。<br />
内容如下：  </p>

<!-- more -->

<p>``` html</p>
<snippet>
    <content>
    &lt;![CDATA[
&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML&gt; 
<html> 
<head> 
    <meta charset="utf-8" /> 
    <title>${1}</title> 
</head>
<body>
    ${1}
</body>
</html>
    ]]&gt;
    </content>
    <!-- Optional: Set a tabTrigger to define how to trigger the snippet -->
    <tabtrigger>myhtml</tabtrigger>
    <!-- Optional: Set a scope to limit where the snippet will trigger -->
    <!-- <scope>source.python</scope> -->
</snippet>
<p>sublime-snippet
```
重启sublime，新建文件输入myhtml，然后按<code>tab</code>。</p>
